<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="K" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Knead" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Knead,</orth> to work into dough: <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 23</bibl>. <cit><quote>--ing up the honey,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.199" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 199</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to become a --ed clod,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.121" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 121</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will k. him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.231" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 231</bibl></cit> (beat him into a jelly).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>